git init
git add filename
git commit -m "Adding files"
git push https://github.com/affablelochan/PhD_thesis


to download the contents of git folder:

git clone https://github.com/affablelochan/PhD_thesis.git

If you think the code changed by other user while you are making changes to code use pull command. 
git pull origin

for the first time

git config --global user.name "affablelochan"
git config --global user.email "affablelochan@gmail.com"



http://classic.scottr.org/presentations/git-in-5-minutes/

